OL,3,CMan dies following road crash
OL,5,FA man who died following a crash in
OL,6,FBallyclare has been named as Matthew
OL,7,FMcIlroy.
OL,9,FPolice said the 31-year-old, who was
OL,10,Ffrom the Co Antrim area, died
OL,11,Ffollowing the single-vehicle collision
OL,12,Fin the Green Road on Friday evening.
OL,14,FA black Audi A5 car was found crashed
OL,15,Fand overturned.
OL,17,FA police spokesperson said: "Police
OL,18,Freceived a report at around 6.45pm on
OL,19,FFriday of a black Audi A5 car which
OL,20,Fhad crashed and overturned in the
OL,21,FGreen Road area.
