OL,3,CMan dies following road crash
OL,5,F"Officers, along with colleagues from
OL,6,Fthe Northern Ireland Ambulance Service
OL,7,Fand Northern Ireland Fire and Rescue
OL,8,FService, attended, however, sadly the
OL,9,Fdriver was pronounced deceased at the
OL,10,Fscene.
OL,12,F"Our inquiries are continuing and we
OL,13,Fwould appeal to anyone who witnessed
OL,14,Fthe collision, or who may have any
OL,15,Finformation which could assist with
OL,16,Four investigation ` including dash-cam
OL,17,For other footage ` contact the
OL,18,Fcollision investigation unit on 101."
